snippet: The United States and dozens of other countries vowed Friday to speed up and strengthen the U.N.'s overstretched peacekeeping response to crises around the world....

headline.print_headline: US, Others Vow to Strengthen UN Peacekeeping
headline.main: US, Others Vow to Strengthen UN Peacekeeping

lead_paragraph: The United States and dozens of other countries vowed Friday to speed up and strengthen the U.N.'s overstretched peacekeeping response to crises around the world.
